But i ran across a huge problem....the skillcapes come up as nulls. I've found a client that has skillcapes: [URL=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,407110.0.html]http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,407110.0.html[/URL]
But they still come up as nulls....so Does this mean it's server side? I found them in my item config as the correct id and don't know where to go from there, if anyone can help that'd be great
